column5: AWESOME!!!!!!!  We just won Gold in the Long Track Speed Skating Mens Pursuit and in the Mens Snowboard Parallel Giant Slalom!!!!!!!!
We had a slow start but boy are we bringing it home now...

We still have a chance at 3 more golds...We're sitting 2nd and 5th going into the last run of four-man bobsled tonight at 5:40, we're in the finals for men's curling tonight at 6:00, and, of course, the finals for men's hockey tomorrow.  We're basically assured of 1st overall in golds!
It seems like we are winning everything (or maybe that is the beauty of watching a Canadian channel). Good for us!!! Jim
Canada adds Mens Curling Gold to the pile!!!!!!
That was very cool to watch.  CONGRATS!
i think the skip on the womans team was alot easier to watch ...  congrates boys ...if you ever visit this site youll get this message
